               <msContents>
                  <summary>This order of arrest is addressed to the chief of police of the village of Dinnis. He is to deliver those individuals who were "wanted" by the tax collectors of Bacchias. If he does not do this he is to come himself along with his assistant.</summary>
                  <msItem>
                     <note type="general">Location: Ann Arbor</note>
