                  <objectDesc>
                     <p>
                        <note type="conservation">This light-brown papyrus is completely preserved and regularly cut on all sides. It has only sustained a little damage in the bottom, where a small strip of papyrus has been chopped off. There is a kollesis on the left edge of the papyrus. Two small pieces of papyrus glued on the bak of the sheet for reinforcement. One of these small pieces contains a little writing and appears to have been cut or torn off from an outdated document. (TC).</note>
                     </p>
